      "rationale": "Predicted NIH compared against measured NIH at all five operating points using a relative error metric. Mean absolute relative error 8.3%; maximum 14.7%. All predictions within the pre-specified 15% tolerance band. Systematic bias assessed and found non-significant (p = 0.23).",
